      "author": "PeterCarterSr",
      "description": "## What's New in v1.1.0\n\n### CRM Layer\n- **Interaction logging**: Log calls, emails, meetings, and notes against any contact from the command palette or People panel\n- **Follow-up reminders**: Set follow-up dates on contacts; hourly background checker fires Obsidian notices for due and overdue follow-ups\n- **CRM frontmatter schema**: Contact notes now include `last-contact`, `next-follow-up`, `deal-stage`, and `follow-up-status` fields\n- **New sort modes**: Sort the People panel by Last Contacted, Follow-up Due, or Deal Stage\n- **Overdue filter**: One-click filter to show only contacts with overdue follow-ups (⏰ button)\n- **Per-contact actions**: Log interaction or set follow-up directly from any contact row in the People panel\n- **Visual indicators**: Contacts with due (🔔) or overdue (⏰) follow-ups are highlighted in the list\n\n### Infrastructure\n- GitHub Actions CI: typecheck + build on every push to main\n- GitHub Actions Release: automated build + release on version tags",
      "downloadCount": 1,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "v1.1.0 — CRM Layer",
